(25691, 400, 2532, 'description', '<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The Sr. Oracle DBA is responsible for providing technical\r\nexpertise in the analysis, design, implementation, and maintenance of an\r\nexisting high-volume, data intensive system.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Knowledge &amp;\r\nExperience</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Minimum of 5 years&rsquo; hands-on experience\r\n     supporting Oracle database 12c and Oracle EBS 12.</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Background in R12.2 application administration is\r\n     required.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Strong knowledge of Oracle 11g/12c internals, from\r\n     performance troubleshooting down to ASM striping.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Strong Database Administration and SQL skills.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Hands on Experience in Exadata</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Operating system knowledge (Unix, Linux and/or Windows).</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Daily administration activities such as storage layout,\r\n     Data Guard replication, backup/restore, patching, maintenance, upgrades,\r\n     and access control should be second nature.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Extensive knowledge of high availability databases.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Proficient with automation of maintenance tasks using\r\n     PL/SQL and other scripting and tools.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Superior troubleshooting skills, battle-tested in\r\n     high-volume production environments including Grid Control Administration.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Hands on experience with Performance tuning, Grid\r\n     Control, analyzing and handling corruption, Backup &amp; recovery,\r\n     installations &amp; configuration.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Hands on experience in RAC, Data Guard and multi tenant\r\n     database.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Virtualization of high-performance database\r\n     environments.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Schema design and access control .</span><br />\r\n     Maintain database backup/recovery procedures and disaster recovery\r\n     database environment.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Develop and support procedures for database security.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Conduct database capacity planning, record archival,\r\n     and performance tuning regularly.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Implement and support database software upgrade and\r\n     patch management procedures.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Develop processes, procedures and guidelines for\r\n     troubleshooting database events and performing sustaining tasks.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Build Oracle environments as needed.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background: whitesmoke">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Preferred Skills</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst">&nbsp;</p><ul><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Excellent verbal and written communication skills</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Excellent customer focus and handling skills</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Strong analytical reasoning and problem solving skills</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Strong focus on diagnosing and resolving complex technical problems</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Strong teamwork skills and ability to work as member of a global\r\nteam</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Results oriented</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to work under pressure in escalated situations</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Coach, mentor, and develop technical team members.</span></li></ul><!--[if !supportLists]--><p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast">&nbsp;</p>', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Duties:</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal">This position will be responsible for monitoring and tuning\r\ndatabase performance. It ensures that data is appropriately protected via\r\ndatabase backup and related strategies.&nbsp;\r\nThe position loads, or assists in loading of, database software, upgrade\r\nand patching.&nbsp; This position will assist\r\nwith the evaluation and selection of infrastructure components and provide\r\noperational support for the database, ensuring data integrity, database\r\navailability, and performance.&nbsp; It will\r\nprovide resolutions to technical problems.&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nThis position will also assist management with short/long-range planning\r\nfor hardware and software changes and additions.&nbsp; It serves as a project lead for software\r\nacquisition or upgrades.&nbsp; This position\r\nwill also administer Oracle 10g, 11g, &amp; 12c stand-alone, RAC(including\r\nExadata), and FailSafe environments on Windows 2003, 2008 R2, and Windows 2012\r\nas well as AIX, RedHat, &amp; Oracle Linux(Exadata) platforms. </p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to work\r\neffectively with Oracle DBAs, developers, and infrastructure teams to resolve\r\nproblems with application/database systems.</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Assist in normal\r\ndatabase daily work requests for Oracle.&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal">Minimum of 10 years Oracle DBA experience.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience working in Database\r\nAdministration for Oracle 10g, 11g, &amp; 12c stand-alone and RAC environments\r\non on Windows 2008 R2 &amp; Windows 2012 with a good working knowledge of\r\nAIX\\Linux.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Oracle database software\r\ninstallation and software patching experience is needed.&nbsp; Must have indepth knowledge of monitoring\r\n(Oracle Cloud Control), tuning and database design standards.&nbsp; Project management skills, ANSI SQL\r\n&amp;PL\\SQL Programming and a working knowledge of ETL operations a bonus.&nbsp;&nbsp; Knowledge of Oracle Golden Gate, Oracle\r\nExadata architecture and Delphix are also highly recommended.</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle RAC (Advanced) &ndash; 4 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->AIX (Advanced) &ndash; 3 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Windows (Advanced) &ndash; 2 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Linux (Advanced) &ndash; 2 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->HP Server Hardware (Intermediate) &ndash; 3 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Dell Server Hardware (Intermediate) &ndash; 3 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle 10g, 11g (Advanced) &ndash; 4 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle 12 C (Advanced) &ndash; 2 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle Golden Gate (Advanced) &ndash; 3 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle Failsafe (Advanced) &ndash; 3 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle Database EE (Advanced) &ndash; 3 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle Data Guard (Advanced) &ndash; 3 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Toad (Intermediate) &ndash; 2 years</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Delphix (Beginner) &ndash; 1 year</p><p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Exadata (Beginner) &ndash; 1 year</p><p style="margin-left: 0.5in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2017-02-21 09:31:53', 1253, 1),
