bs/).</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Some of the current projects to be addressed include:<span>&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&bull;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Up\r\nconverting HL7 message from 2.1, 2.2, 2.3 to 2.3.1 or 2.5.1</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&bull;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Converting\r\nCSV files to HL7 2.3.1</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&bull;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Splitting\r\nHL7 files by lab<a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a> result.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">This position is a three month CDC grant funded position.\r\nThis position is not expected to continue after July 1st, 2017.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><u>Essential Duties/Responsibilities:</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">1.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Serve as\r\na key resource during for converting HL7 messages with Rhapsody.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">2.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Work with\r\nlaboratories in their efforts to improve what they send in their HL7 messages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><u>Job Requirements:</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">1.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Proven\r\nanalytical and technical or project documentation skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">2.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Three\r\nYears of relevant experience with Orion Rhapsody</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">3.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Experience\r\nin public health, HL7, or medical related industry. (Preferred)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">4.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs