(26062, 400, 2552, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">Key\r\nResponsibilities:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">Enhance\r\nexisting </span><a href="http://ck.net/"><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: blue; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">CK.NET</span></a><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt"> WPF\r\napplication to support business functions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1.8pt 0.55in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 110%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">Understand the business requirements and look for ways to optimize the\r\ndatabase management <br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.65pt">processes,\r\nmonthly and ad hoc reports, and tool sets established to support the El\r\nprogram.</span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.1in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 112%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.75pt">Assess existing program and data management processes and identify\r\npotential efficiency upgrades, </span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.6pt">such as translating SQL scripts into stored procedures and converting\r\nstandalone MS Access applications </span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">into integrated tools.</span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.75pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.1in 0.0001pt 0.55in; text-indent: -0.3in; line-height: 111%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">Develop SSRS reports and queries as needed and make recommendations for\r\nstreamlining / automating </span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.6pt">existing reporting processes.</span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1.8pt 0in 0.0001pt 0.55in; text-indent: -0.3in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.8pt">Execute\r\nlegacy SQL scripts to upload, analyze, and validate data submitted by the El\r\nprograms.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.3in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 111%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.5pt">Assist the EDS Data Manager by performing operational activities, such as\r\nmonthly payment voucher </span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.6pt">processing for El programs.</span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.5pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1.8pt 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">Participate\r\nin troubleshooting system issues and data problems as needed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1.8pt 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.95pt">Prepare\r\ndocumentation of existing functions and any approved enhancements.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1.8pt 0.3in 0.0001pt 0.55in; text-indent: -0.3in; line-height: 112%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">Provide support during the design, development, testing and migration\r\nphases as we move from the </span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">current legacy processes to web-based application environment.</span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.4in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.5pt">Assist with data migration activities to move legacy data to the future\r\nweb-based system when it is </span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.6pt">available.</span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.5pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1.8pt 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.55pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 1pt">Perform\r\nother miscellaneous operational activities as required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-top: 12.6pt; line-height: 81%" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 81%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.6pt">Technical Skills:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1.8pt 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"