(26112, 400, 2555, 'description', '<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Respond and resolve tickets and incidents in\r\naccordance with EOHHS IT policies and procedures as they relate to customer\r\nsupport and updates</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Maintain inventories of all EOHHS IT assets\r\nusing the EOHHS inventory collection process to secure Commonwealth assets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Manage the upgrade of hardware &amp; software\r\nwhen necessary to insure that all services are provided in a secure and timely\r\nfashion.&nbsp; This includes but is not\r\nlimited to new Anti-Virus, Operating System patches, or other mandated software\r\nupgrades as directed by EOHHS standards and practices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Clearly communicate and/or escalate to their\r\nsupervisor any IT operations issues or disruptions (planned or unplanned) to\r\nminimize user impact.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Assist Telecom with movement of IP phones as\r\nrequired.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Work collaboratively with internal and external\r\ngroups in a team environment to improve overall customer service and\r\nsupport.&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Provide / Utilize any and all resources\r\navailable through EOHHS and other sources for assistance with problem\r\nresolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Implementation of\r\nEOHHS IT enterprise images for Desktops /Laptops according to EOHHS procedures\r\nand policy to insure a consistent environment. </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Responsible for timely\r\nresponse and support during scheduled and authorized non-business hours to\r\ninsure continuity of services to the network environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Install and move assets as required according to\r\nEOHHS policies and procedures</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Assist / lead with meetings special projects and\r\nother requests as required to maximize the efficient use of IT resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Complete all activities within EOHHS security\r\npolicies and practices to insure the safety and privacy of data, its clients\r\nand its resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Act as the contact person for office\r\nwiring/cable installations and performs related duties as required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Required to travel to various sites as needed or\r\nrequested.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Participate in team meetings as required</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Manage site specific projects as related to\r\nnetwork infrastructure &amp; server support </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Install, configure and support state issued\r\nmobile devices </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Troubleshooting and resolving Network issues and\r\ninfrastructure as required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Configure and maintain backup and restore\r\nprocess to include swapping tapes, restoring files, and transfer of media in\r\naccordance with EOHHS policies and procedures</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Support, trouble shoot and configure remote\r\naccess to assist network users with connectivi