(26199, 400, 2537, 'description', '<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Duties</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Incumbent works in the Department of Child\r\nServices (DCS), Child Support Bureau (CSB) IT Office, and is responsible for\r\napplication and networking architecture activities for the child support\r\nsystems - Indiana Support Enforcement Tracking System (ISETS) and the future\r\nIndiana Verification and Enforcement of Support (INvest) system.&nbsp; The\r\nSystem Architect Specialist reports to the Chief Architect/Application Systems\r\nAnalyst and Programming Manager.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Representative duties include</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Completes\r\nenvironmental analysis of system needs and requirements of existing and\r\nproposed system solutions (BPM, JAVA) and develops architectural and technical\r\ndesigns and specifications;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Analyzes technical\r\nneeds, requirements, and state of the network&rsquo;s infrastructure design,\r\nintegration,&nbsp; operations and develops documentation and diagrams;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provides direction\r\nand subject matter expertise on integration architectures and technologies such\r\nas SOA, ESB, Web Services, Micro Services, JavaScript, XML, JSON etc.;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Consults with and\r\nmakes recommendations to business and technical groups at all levels to\r\nevaluate architectural and functional requirements, evaluate technology needs,\r\nand formulate solutions;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Creates and maintains\r\nlogical and physical architecture modeling and diagrams;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Evaluates technology\r\nand products to determine the feasibility of adding to CSB IT standards;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Participates in and\r\nworks with the vendor on system design walk-throughs for INvest;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Graphically and\r\nverbally communicates application concepts;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Discerns\r\nbusiness/technical needs as it relates to child support applications;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Develops and enforces\r\narchitecture strategies and policies for long-term planning and implementation;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Works with current\r\nApplication and Data Architect on project assignments;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Continues to develop\r\nworking knowledge of the child support solutions;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Performs other\r\nrelated duties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Job\r\nRequirements</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge: of JAVA, BPM Suite, DB2 LUW, and AIX on P Series;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of adoption and implementation of SOA including design and run-time\r\ngovernance;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of web service technologies like JAX-WS, WSDL, XML, JSON;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of application communications, connectivity and security;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of</span><span class="st1"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #545454"> </span></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">designing\r\nnetworks, including local area networks (LANs), wide area networks (WANs), the\r\nInternet, intranets, and other data communication systems;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of network security, SSL, Proxy, Load Balancing;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nthe most recent technology trends and new developments in software\r\narchitecture;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nJavaScript front-end technologies like Angular, React;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\ncomputer hardware/software capabilities and configurations;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nUML and other modeling methods;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to read and\r\nunderstand complicated technical documentation and perform logic analysis;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to\r\ncommunicate effectively, both orally and in writing;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to guide and\r\ncoordinate the work of others.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Difficulty of Work</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Incumbent applies general agency guidelines\r\nin designing and maintaining system architectures for a variety of complex\r\ntechnology areas, using considerable judgment in selecting those techniques and\r\nprocedures most pertinent.&nbsp; Hardware and software problems faced are\r\nnon-routine in nature and require in-depth analysis and application of advanced\r\nlogic to reach a solution, which may be unique in the field.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Responsibility</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Incumbent works with minimum supervision and\r\nmakes many individual judgments in achieving general goals.&nbsp; Work is\r\nreviewed for attainment of objectives and compliance with policy.&nbsp;\r\nIncumbent&rsquo;s contribution may have a significant impact on the policies and\r\npractices of CSB, and the decisions made by management.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Personal Work Relationships</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Contacts are with information technology\r\nstaff within and outside the agency and department for the purpose of\r\nfacilitating communication of requirements and responsibilities for systems\r\nunder development or evaluation.&nbsp; Incumbent communicates with the public\r\nconcerning system input and output.&nbsp; Incumbent is involved in cooperative\r\nproblem solving in highly sensitive or disputed situations.</span></p>', '<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Duties</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Incumbent works in the Department of Child\r\nServices (DCS), Child Support Bureau (CSB) IT Office, and is responsible for\r\napplication and networking architecture activities for the child support\r\nsystems - Indiana Support Enforcement Tracking System (ISETS) and the future\r\nIndiana Verification and Enforcement of Support (INvest) system.&nbsp; The\r\nSystem Architect Specialist reports to the Chief Architect/Application Systems\r\nAnalyst and Programming Manager.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Representative duties include</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Completes\r\nenvironmental analysis of system needs and requirements of existing and\r\nproposed system solutions (BPM, JAVA) and develops architectural and technical\r\ndesigns and specifications;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Analyzes technical\r\nneeds, requirements, and state of the network&rsquo;s infrastructure design,\r\nintegration,&nbsp; operations and develops documentation and diagrams;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Provides direction\r\nand subject matter expertise on integration architectures and technologies such\r\nas SOA, ESB, Web Services, Micro Services, JavaScript, XML, JSON etc.;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Consults with and\r\nmakes recommendations to business and technical groups at all levels to\r\nevaluate architectural and functional requirements, evaluate technology needs,\r\nand formulate solutions;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Creates and maintains\r\nlogical and physical architecture modeling and diagrams;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Evaluates technology\r\nand products to determine the feasibility of adding to CSB IT standards;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Participates in and\r\nworks with the vendor on system design walk-throughs for INvest;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Graphically and\r\nverbally communicates application concepts;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Discerns\r\nbusiness/technical needs as it relates to child support applications;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Develops and enforces\r\narchitecture strategies and policies for long-term planning and implementation;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Works with current\r\nApplication and Data Architect on project assignments;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Continues to develop\r\nworking knowledge of the child support solutions;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Performs other\r\nrelated duties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Job\r\nRequirements</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge: of JAVA, BPM Suite, DB2 LUW, and AIX on P Series;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of adoption and implementation of SOA including design and run-time\r\ngovernance;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of web service technologies like JAX-WS, WSDL, XML, JSON;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of application communications, connectivity and security;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of</span><span class="st1"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #545454"> </span></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">designing\r\nnetworks, including local area networks (LANs), wide area networks (WANs), the\r\nInternet, intranets, and other data communication systems;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Must have advanced\r\nknowledge of network security, SSL, Proxy, Load Balancing;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nthe most recent technology trends and new developments in software\r\narchitecture;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nJavaScript front-end technologies like Angular, React;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\ncomputer hardware/software capabilities and configurations;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nUML and other modeling methods;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Ability to read and\r\nunderstand complicated technical documentation and perform logic analysis;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Ability to\r\ncommunicate effectively, both orally and in writing;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Ability to guide and\r\ncoordinate the work of others.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Difficulty of Work</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Incumbent applies general agency guidelines\r\nin designing and maintaining system architectures for a variety of complex\r\ntechnology areas, using considerable judgment in selecting those techniques and\r\nprocedures most pertinent.&nbsp; Hardware and software problems faced are\r\nnon-routine in nature and require in-depth analysis and application of advanced\r\nlogic to reach a solution, which may be unique in the field.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Responsibility</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Incumbent works with minimum supervision and\r\nmakes many individual judgments in achieving general goals.&nbsp; Work is\r\nreviewed for attainment of objectives and compliance with policy.&nbsp;\r\nIncumbent&rsquo;s contribution may have a significant impact on the policies and\r\npractices of CSB, and the decisions made by management.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Personal Work Relationships</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Contacts are with information technology\r\nstaff within and outside the agency and department for the purpose of\r\nfacilitating communication of requirements and responsibilities for systems\r\nunder development or evaluation.&nbsp; Incumbent communicates with the public\r\nconcerning system input and output.&nbsp; Incumbent is involved in cooperative\r\nproblem solving in highly sensitive or disputed situations.</span></p>', NULL, '2017-03-17 14:49:41', 180, 1),
