(26449, 400, 2574, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Scope\r\nof position</u></strong><u><span style="font-size: 12pt"></span></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">We are seeking a senior software developer with at least 8\r\nyears&rsquo; experience in web application support and development with database\r\ndesign skills in a Microsoft .NET/SQL environment to join a highly skilled\r\nAgile team in a fast-paced environment converting legacy applications and\r\nsupporting existing ones.&nbsp; This candidate must have a strong development\r\nbackground developing and understanding solutions written in C# and strong\r\ndebugging skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Primary Responsibilities</u></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->8-10 years&rsquo; experience developing large systems\r\non the Microsoft stack.<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience with Entity Framework, LINQ and\r\nLambda Expressions</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must be able to design, build, and maintain\r\nefficient, reusable, and reliable C# code</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience in cloud-based development\r\nenvironments</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience with contemporary REST/web services\r\ndevelopment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must have excellent interpersonal and\r\ncommunication skills both written and verbal with self-motivation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must be able to identify bottlenecks and bugs,\r\nand devise solutions to these problems </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to work individually or within a team\r\nenvironment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to develop technology projects and\r\nsolutions using Agile Scrum Framework; including prototyping, technical design,\r\nand specifications determined from business requirement documents </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to manage priorities in a fast-paced\r\nenvironment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Excellent attention to details</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Solid understanding of Object Oriented analysis\r\nand design </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to take direction, constructive\r\ncriticism and work to specified deadlines, with the ability to execute\r\ndevelopment code with limited guidance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Implement programming changes to production\r\nfollowing system life cycle and release strategy procedures</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Facilitate with development within the new\r\nenvironments, utilizing the latest Microsoft stack, as needed</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Familiarity with source control software: Team\r\nFoundation Server (TFS)<strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif"></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Skills/Abilities/Experience &amp; Qualifications</u>:</strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif"></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0in">\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Windows/Web\r\n     Development: VB.NET 2010 and greater, ASP.NET 2010 and greater</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Database:\r\n     SQL 2014 Server and ability to work with older SQL Server versions</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Strong\r\n     proficiency in C#, with fair knowledge of the language specification</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Strong\r\n     Object Oriented design and development</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Worked\r\n     on projects with MVC 5 and above</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Enterprise\r\n     Development: .NET, XML, JSON, Web Services, WCF, Linq</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Full\r\n     stack developer (C#, VB.NET, Entity Framework/Entity Framework Core,\r\n     ASP.NET, WEBAPI, Web Services, SQL Server)</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Work\r\n     on Bootstrap is a plus</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Experience\r\n     with Agile Scrum</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Scope\r\nof position</u></strong><u></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">We are seeking a senior software developer with at least 8\r\nyears&rsquo; experience in web application support and development with database\r\ndesign skills in a Microsoft .NET/SQL environment to join a highly skilled\r\nAgile team in a fast-paced environment converting legacy applications and\r\nsupporting existing ones.&nbsp; This candidate must have a strong development\r\nbackground developing and understanding solutions written in C# and strong\r\ndebugging skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Primary Responsibilities</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->8-10 years&rsquo; experience developing large systems\r\non the Microsoft stack.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience with Entity Framework, LINQ and\r\nLambda Expressions</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must be able to design, build, and maintain\r\nefficient, reusable, and reliable C# code</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience in cloud-based development\r\nenvironments</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience with contemporary REST/web services\r\ndevelopment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must have excellent interpersonal and\r\ncommunication skills both written and verbal with self-motivation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must be able to identify bottlenecks and bugs,\r\nand devise solutions to these problems </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to work individually or within a team\r\nenvironment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to develop technology projects and\r\nsolutions using Agile Scrum Framework; including prototyping, technical design,\r\nand specifications determined from business requirement documents </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to manage priorities in a fast-paced\r\nenvironment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Excellent attention to details</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Solid understanding of Object Oriented analysis\r\nand design </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''