(26548, 400, 2567, 'description', '<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<h2>Essential Duties/Responsibilities:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Manage the Software Development Life Cycle\r\n(SDLC) for <span style="color: black">.Net</span>, iOS, and\r\nAndroid programming languages</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Leads and directs a team of analyst and\r\ndevelopers responsible for IOT applications development</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Evaluates\r\nexisting and potential new applications to determine scope of request, cost,\r\nschedules, and resources</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Relies on extensive experience and judgement to\r\nplan and accomplish goals</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>A wide degree of creativity and latitude is\r\nrequired</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Have knowledge of Team Foundation Server and/or\r\nthe Atlassian Suite for managing SDLC work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Manages,\r\nmaintains, and monitors project plans, timelines, QA, and UAT phases</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Directs preparation of analyses, plans, and\r\nverification procedures for applications</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Job Requirements:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Responsible for facilitating scrums, sprint\r\nplanning, sprint demo and retrospective meetings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Possess conflict resolution, does conversation\r\nby focusing on scrum values of openness, honesty, and respect</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Should be a friendly communicative person,\r\nbecause when team is moving fast in Agile, communication is the effective force\r\nwhich holds the team together</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Needs to forecast the numbers of deliverables\r\npossible in an iteration, which is based on evidence and reliable source</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Needs to be expert in estimation and planning. <span style="color: black">Will </span>know how to create useful,\r\nreliable and practical plans for software development projects</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Should be a good coach in Agile practices. They\r\ncan coach individuals and interactions over processes and tools</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Help team or individual to clarify goals and\r\nactions to achieve them</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Ability to shield his team from outside\r\ndistractions and interferences</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Ability to ensure the correct use of scrum\r\nprocess</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Ability to track and remove impediments</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Needs\r\nto ensure that user experience and the customer&rsquo;s business needs are being\r\nfulfilled</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Excellent\r\ncommunication skills; need the ability to communicate effectively with\r\ndifferent roles, and also have the ability to communicate with different\r\npersonality-types.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Ability\r\nto have a realistic vision of what success of the product means and ensure that\r\nthis vision becomes reality &ndash; whatever it takes</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Prioritize\r\nthe backlog by understanding the relative business value of each feature</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Be\r\npassionate about the quality of the product</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Technical Skill Requirements:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Agile Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Planning Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span>Stakeholder Management, Negotiation &amp;\r\nCommunication Skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Team\r\nFoundation Server and/or JIRA/Confluence experience</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Lead\r\nor developed a .Net, <span>&nbsp;</span>iOS, and/or Android\r\napplication engagement</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Demonstrated\r\nproficiency using standard office software applications, query and control\r\nlanguages, programming languages, and database systems</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style="color: black">Understands\r\nprototyping tools</span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignCellWithSp/>\r\n   <w:DontBreakConstrainedForcedTables/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignInTxbx/>\r\n   <w:Word11KerningPairs/>\r\n   <w:CachedColBalance/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <m:mathPr>\r\n   <m:mathFont m:val="Cambria Math"/>\r\n   <m:brkBin m:val="before"/>\r\n   <m:brkBinSub m:val="&#45;-"/>\r\