(26564, 400, 2596, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Responsibilities </span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0in">\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Primary initial responsibility is for\r\n     management of a project. Focuses on meeting project commitments, including\r\n     communications with sponsors, stakeholders, etc. Spends significant time\r\n     on project management responsibilities. As assigned, lead or assist in the\r\n     planning and implementation.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Work in conjunction with the Business to\r\n     facilitate the definition of service levels and customer requirements.\r\n     Interact with existing or potential stakeholders and the Business to\r\n     determine their needs and to develop plans for improving delivery.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Strong verbal, analytical and written\r\n     communication skills are required</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Follows a defined EOHHS IT project management\r\n     methodology. Present oral and written reports defining plans, problems and\r\n     resolutions to appropriate levels of management.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Support stakeholders in design, priority\r\n     setting and implementation according to the Business&rsquo; strategic\r\n     initiatives. </span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Identifies opportunities for\r\n     improving and streamlining IT processes as well as eliminating security\r\n     risks (compliance)<strong></strong></span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Responsible for identifying the\r\n     required project resources; for their technical or functional development,\r\n     performance, and/or termination during the project.<strong></strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Qualifications </span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Valid driver&rsquo;s license and access to vehicle</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0in">\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Minimum 5 years of increasingly responsible\r\n     experience, including experience successfully managing various projects\r\n     (in &lsquo;healthcare&rsquo; &ndash; preferred). Outstanding grasp of information technology\r\n     concepts and processes. Demonstrated aptitude for effective leadership of\r\n     staff. (PMP certification preferred).</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Strong issue &amp; problem management skills,\r\n     including root cause analysis and troubleshooting skills.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Capable of working independently or as part of\r\n     a large team</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Demonstrated leadership with strong\r\n     organizational, presentation and customer service skills</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Experience working in a PMO environment</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Project Portfolio Management experience</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Understanding of software development lifecycle\r\n     methodologies</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Demonstrated ability to conduct detailed\r\n     planning, perform risk assessments, and successfully mitigate project\r\n     risks </span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">Ability to relate IT program priorities to the\r\n     Business</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif