(26853, 400, 2614, 'description', '<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Position Summary:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt">Qualifications</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Respond and\r\nresolve tickets and incidents in accordance with EOHHS IT policies and\r\nprocedures as they relate to customer support and updates</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Maintain\r\ninventories of all EOHHS IT assets using the EOHHS inventory collection process\r\nto secure Commonwealth assets.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Manage the\r\nupgrade of hardware &amp; software when necessary to insure that all services\r\nare provided in a secure and timely fashion.&nbsp;\r\nThis includes but is not limited to new Anti-Virus, Operating System\r\npatches, or other mandated software upgrades as directed by EOHHS standards and\r\npractices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Clearly\r\ncommunicate and/or escalate to their supervisor any IT operations issues or\r\ndisruptions (planned or unplanned) to minimize user impact.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Assist Telecom\r\nwith movement of IP phones as required.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Work\r\ncollaboratively with internal and external groups in a team environment to\r\nimprove overall customer service and support.&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Provide /\r\nUtilize any and all resources available through EOHHS and other sources for\r\nassistance with problem resolution.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Implementation\r\nof EOHHS IT enterprise images for Desktops /Laptops according to EOHHS\r\nprocedures and policy to insure a consistent environment. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Responsible\r\nfor timely response and support during scheduled and authorized non-business\r\nhours to insure continuity of services to the network environment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Install and\r\nmove assets as required according to EOHHS policies and procedures</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Assist / lead\r\nwith meetings special projects and other requests as required to maximize the\r\nefficient use of IT resources.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Complete all\r\nactivities within EOHHS security policies and practices to insure the safety\r\nand privacy of data, its clients and its resources.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Act as the\r\ncontact person for office wiring/cable installations and performs related\r\nduties as required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Required to\r\ntravel to various sites as needed or requested.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Participate in\r\nteam meetings as required</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Manage site specific\r\nprojects as related to network infrastructure &amp; server support </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Install,\r\nconfigure and support state issued mobile devices </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Troubleshooting\r\nand resolving Network issues and infrastructure as required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Configure and\r\nmaintain backup and restore process to include swapping tapes, restoring files,\r\nand transfer of media in accordance with EOHHS policies and procedures</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Support,\r\ntrouble shoot and configure remote access to assist network users with\r\nconnectivity to EOHHS network from non-magnet connections.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Participate in\r\nthe development of the documentation of servers, infrastructure and practices\r\nby providing written and/or verbal communications to effectively maintain a\r\nresource of standard practices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Provide\r\nconsultative IT services to IT management and site teams as needed</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Mentor other IT\r\nprofessionals to insure their professional growth and skill set improvement</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Utilize Network\r\nAdministrative Tools to manage the network and ensure efficiency of system\r\nresources</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Build and\r\nrestore severs as required</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Maintain\r\nDisaster recovery package for server rooms as required</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Review server\r\nevent logs on a daily basis to ensure optimal performance and identify\r\npotential issues</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 10pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%" class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Perform\r\nall duties as required and directed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 10pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%" class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Valid\r\ndriver&rsquo;s license and access to a vehicle </span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt">Requirements</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 2.9pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Accomplishment\r\nand proficiency in performing all general and detailed responsibilities and\r\nduties </span><span style="font-size: 10pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Ability\r\nto work independently with limited direct supervision as needed to accomplish\r\nthe responsibilities of the position</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Ability\r\nto monitor desktops / Servers and associated network performance</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Working\r\nknowledge of how IT Operations group supports the agency&rsquo;s business needs</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Working\r\nknowledge of Helpdesk systems</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Knowledge\r\nof the reporting structure and workings of state government</span><span style="font-size: 10pt"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Skill growth\r\nand knowledge attainment in emerging technologies</span></p>', '<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Position Summary:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt">Qualifications</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Respond and\r\nresolve tickets and incidents in accordance with EOHHS IT policies and\r\nprocedures as they relate to customer support and updates</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Maintain\r\ninventories of all EOHHS IT assets using the EOHHS inventory collection process\r\nto secure Commonwealth assets.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Manage the\r\nupgrade of hardware &amp; software when necessary to insure that all services\r\nare provided in a secure and timely fashion.&nbsp;\r\nThis includes but is not limited to new Anti-Virus, Operating System\r\npatches, or other mandated software upgrades as directed by EOHHS standards and\r\npractices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Clearly\r\ncommunicate and/or escalate to their supervisor any IT operations issues or\r\ndisruptions (planned or unplanned) to minimize user impact.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Assist Telecom\r\nwith movement of IP phones as required.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Work\r\ncollaboratively with internal and external groups in a team environment to\r\nimprove overall customer service and support.&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Provide /\r\nUtilize any and all resources available through EOHHS and other sources for\r\nassistance with problem resolution.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Implementation\r\nof EOHHS IT enterprise images for Desktops /Laptops according to EOHHS\r\nprocedures and policy to insure a consistent environment. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Responsible\r\nfor timely response and support during scheduled and authorized non-business\r\nhours to insure continuity of services to the network environment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Install and\r\nmove assets as required according to EOHHS policies and procedures</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Assist / lead\r\nwith meetings special projects and other requests as required to maximize the\r\nefficient use of IT resources.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Complete all\r\nactivities within EOHHS security policies and practices to insure the safety\r\nand privacy of data, its clients and its resources.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Act as the\r\ncontact person for office wiring/cable installations and performs related\r\nduties as required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Required to\r\ntravel to various sites as needed or requested.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Participate in\r\nteam meetings as required</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Manage site specific\r\nprojects as related to network infrastructure &amp; server support </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Install,\r\nconfigure and support state issued mobile devices </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Troubleshooting\r\nand resolving Network issues and infrastructure as required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Configure and\r\nmaintain backup and restore process to include swapping tapes, restoring files,\r\nand transfer of media in accordance with EOHHS policies and procedures</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Support,\r\ntrouble shoot and configure remote access to assist network users with\r\nconnectivity to EOHHS network from non-magnet connections.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Participate in\r\nthe development of the documentation of servers, infrastructure and practices\r\nby providing written and/or verbal communications to effectively maintain a\r\nresource of standard practices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Provide\r\nconsultative IT services to IT management and site teams as needed</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Mentor other IT\r\nprofessionals to insure their professional growth and skill set improvement</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Utilize Network\r\nAdministrative Tools to manage the network and ensure efficiency of system\r\nresources</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Build and\r\nrestore severs as required</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Maintain\r\nDisaster recovery package for server rooms as required</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 12pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Review server\r\nevent logs on a daily basis to ensure optimal performance and identify\r\npotential issues</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 10pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%" class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Perform\r\nall duties as required and directed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 10pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%" class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Valid\r\ndriver&rsquo;s license and access to a vehicle </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt">Requirements</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 2.9pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Accomplishment\r\nand proficiency in performing all general and detailed responsibilities and\r\nduties </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt">Ability\r\nto work independently with limited direct supervision as needed to accomplish\r\nthe responsibilities of the position</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><