(26934, 400, 2617, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Description of\r\nDuties:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->System functional design, technical design, and\r\nprogramming experience with a Statewide Automated Child Welfare Information\r\nSystem (SACWIS). Strong understanding of SACWIS functionality. Knowledgeable of\r\ndata structures and data relationships within SACWIS application systems.\r\nStrong understanding of child welfare business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Expertise with full software development life\r\ncycle including software system analysis, functional design, technical design,\r\ndevelopment, testing, code review and production system support.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Software design and development expertise with\r\nn-tier application system architecture including use of Microsoft Visual Studio\r\n.NET 2013, Microsoft SQL Server Enterprise 2008 R2 or 2012, and Microsoft SQL\r\nServer Reporting Services including SSRS, SSIS, and SSAS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Expertise with ASP.Net, MVC 4, Entity Framework\r\n6, JQuery and WCF</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Knowledgeable of software design and development\r\nin Microsoft SQL Server 2008 + database environment using SQL and T-SQL for\r\nstored procedures and functions. Knowledgeable of data analysis and data\r\ndesign. Knowledgeable of performance tuning database stored procedures and\r\nfunctions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Expertise with software design and development\r\nin Microsoft SQL Server 2008 + database environments with Microsoft Visual Studio\r\n.NET including C#, ASP.NET, and XML web services. Strong understanding of .NET\r\nFramework. Experience using Microsoft Team Foundation Server 2013 for system\r\nsource control and configuration management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt;