tabase in large Unix/AIX environment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge in the use of tools and utilities to perform Oracle Database\r\nadministration in Unix environment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge to install, maintain and customize Oracle Application\r\nDevelopment Tools used to development information systems.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge in capacity planning and disaster recovery.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nExtensive knowledge of computer hardware/software capabilities, configuration,\r\nequipment and operation.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge in Oracle database performance and tuning techniques.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge of relational database and design techniques and modeling\r\nprocesses.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge of application software components in the Oracle Database\r\nenvironment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge of computer programming, including computer languages and\r\ntesting of programs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nAbility to gain knowledge of functions and administration of 3rd party\r\nproducts, (Code 1, Micro Focus Cobol, Geographic Coding Plus) used to support\r\ninformation system.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge to maintain Returns Processing System (RPS) system\r\narchitecture including; Reporting, Batch and Printing.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge of policies, standards, procedures and techniques. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough knowledge of Application and Communication Servers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nThorough problem-solving and analytical skills.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nAbility to communicate effectively, both verbally and in writing.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nAbility to read and understand complicated technical manuals.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nAbility to apply theories, principles and methodologies to existing computer\r\nsoftware.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nAbility to write complex database computer programs, macros, scripts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nAbility to work in team unit, independently and on special projects.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&bull;&nbsp;\r\nAbility to establish and maintain a cooperative working relationship with\r\nothers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoN