(27072, 400, 2638, 'description', '<p style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background: whitesmoke" class="MsoNormal"><img src="https://skilldemand.mymailsrvr.com/a/attachments/INBOX/18034/3?wsid=d8b7dc4be779c1ef47b2c1d63bf5eb96116391a0" alt="" /></p>', '<p>The Software development Engineer is expected to:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Create robust and scalable designs that are easily incorporated into the feature and meets customer requirement.&nbsp;</li><li>Develop exemplary code for multiple feature components that meets the company''s best practice standards.&nbsp;</li><li>Deliver code that is stable, secure, on schedule and contained minimal bugs.&nbsp;</li><li>Develop code taking into consideration the &quot;ilities&quot; - scalability, reliability, maintainability, flexibility, etc.&nbsp;</li><li>Write unit test cases for each function for the feature component that effectively excercises the code, surfaces bugs or design issues and integrates with or components those used by Test organization.&nbsp;</li><li>Develop code for feature component conforms to group coding standards, is consistent with product design and architecture goals, does not repeat mistakes, and meets schedule and quality expectations.&nbsp;</li><li>When modifying existing code take necessary steps to fix the code and ensure it meets team and company coding and quality standards.&nbsp;</li><li>Ensures that the delivered overall user experience conforms to the feature objectives.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Core responsibilities pertaining to the job involve:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>&nbsp;Design and develop Data Structures and ETL processes in a SQL Server enviornment;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;Design and develop data structures and ETL Processes using, HIVE, hBase, PIG Scripts, Java functions, Spark with Scala;&nbsp;</li><li>Hadoop Development and implementation;</li><li>Loading from disparate data sets;</li><li>Pre-processing using Hive and Pig;</li><li>Designing, building, installing, configuring, and supporting Hadoop.&nbsp;</li><li>Help build Hadoop Clusters;</li><li>Test prototypes and oversee handover to operational teams;</li><li>Assist in data analysis and data modelling using HIVE;</li><li>Work with product teams to understand requirements and convert them into final product;</li><li>Involved with full software development lifecycle including testing, implementation and auditing in a Agile eniviornment;</li><li>Diagnose and address issues as necessary and work with product teams to implement correction plan.&nbsp;</li></ul>', '(USER) changed field(s): description.', '2017-05-10 09:53:46', 1253, 1),
