!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Deliver completed test plans and test results for the\r\nmultiple feature components as scheduled;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Modifying existing tests and test plans and takes\r\nnecessary steps to fix the test(s) and ensure it meets team and company quality\r\nstandards;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Gather functional and non-functional test requirement\r\nworking with business and operational team to meet the requirement and\r\nsuccessfully validate the release;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Alert development team to product design inconsistencies\r\nand deviations from standards;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Conduct triage cycle for each of issue identified and\r\nfollow through the successful closure;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Work closely with the release management team to have a\r\nrelease certified and scheduled for production;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">work with the deployment and release management team to\r\nsuccessfully deploy the build in test environment and maintain the integrity of\r\nthe environments;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Provide input in developing quality assurance standards\r\nin regards to functional, regression, performance and load testing;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Ensure that the delivered overall user experience\r\nconforms to the feature objectives;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Incorporate automated testing tools and test frameworks as\r\nstandard practice;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Code functions, classes, and methods to support automated\r\ntests for HP QTP, HP Load runner, and Visual Studio; and</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Identify, analyze, and report test results for automated\r\ntest scripts using the automated test tools set;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Responsible for creating acceptance criteria and creating\r\nand tracking all software bugs during Unit, QA, UAT and Production.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.55in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Qualification: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 16.2pt 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Bachelor''s or Master''s degree in Computer Engineering,\r\nComputer Information Systems, or related field;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-s