(27092, 400, 2642, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Description of Duties</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt" class="MsoNormal">The resource will work on a development/maintenance team supporting\r\nDepartment of Revenue, Motor Carrier Services applications on the Intranet and\r\nInternet.&nbsp; Duties will include ongoing\r\nsupport of existing applications; working with business analysts on\r\nenhancements; and new development projects to build applications for all\r\ncommercial motor carrier related functions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt" class="MsoNormal">Requirements are as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Applicant must have a\r\nBS in Computer Science/Information Technology/Computer Engineering or related\r\nfield.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->7+ years of advanced\r\nexperience with development, enhancements, maintenance of Oracle Forms 10g/11g\r\nin a&nbsp; 3-tier environment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Expert knowledge\r\n&amp; implement complex SQL, PL/SQL packages, procedures, functions, and\r\ntriggers using Oracle 11g/12c with 7+ years&rsquo; experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Expert knowledge of\r\nuse of Oracle 11g/12c new features of SQL*Plus, PL/SQL, and Tuning required</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->7+ years advanced\r\nexperience with development, enhancements, maintenance of Oracle Reports\r\n11g/12c in a&nbsp; 3-tier environment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience working\r\nwith Oracle 10g/11g databases required</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-var