(27095, 400, 2644, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Description of Duties:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Understand client\r\nexpectations, requirements, and the business value they expect.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Facilitate\r\nrequirements-gathering workshops with clients.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Construct\r\nhigh-level prod<a name="_GoBack"></a>uct epics and features. Incorporate your\r\nAgile experience navigating the SDLC and pull from your experience using Scrum,\r\nLean, Kanban, TDD and/or XP to ensure success.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Develop\r\nfeatures into user stories that are granular enough for a sprint and convey the\r\ngoals and vision for each sprint.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Craft\r\nand manage a product backlog that clearly articulates all aspects of the user\r\nrequirements and define well-formed acceptance criteria.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Prioritizes\r\nwork within an agile team and maintain a backlog of future work for\r\nconsideration/prioritization.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Translates\r\nbusiness needs/objectives into specific stories and related acceptance\r\ncriteria.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Responsible\r\nfor providing business and process expertise to ensure an agile team has a full\r\nunderstanding of the requirements and business objectives related to the\r\nproduct/solution being developed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Work\r\nwith your team to estimate effort to deliver client requirements and help\r\ncreate proposal/business development artifacts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Coordinate\r\ncommunication between development teams and client stakeholders regarding\r\ngoals, requirements and business needs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Collaborate\r\nwith the development team to define, design, accept and adapt features; ensure\r\neach iteration delivers expected result</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Lead\r\nAgile ceremonies with distributed design and development teams.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Work\r\nwith the Scrum Master and the team with Backlog Refinement, Sprint Planning,\r\nand Sprint Review ceremonies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Define\r\nand manage release plans.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Be\r\nthe primary resource for questions about the details of the projects through\r\ninteraction with internal resources, clients, and stakeholders.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif"