(27140, 400, 2627, 'description', '<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">POSITION PURPOSE</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The JD Edwards Business\r\nAnalyst will be actively involved in the ongoing maintenance and leading\r\nefforts to improve/enhance company&rsquo;s JD Edwards Enterprise One system. This\r\nwill require close interaction with both functional business owners and\r\ntechnical team members to document, gain consensus, and implement changes.\r\nExpertise across a broad range of processes including both Supply Chain and\r\nFinancial processes within JDE will be required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">ESSENTIAL DUTIES</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Lead implementation of future\r\n     project releases and enhancements</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Assist with future software\r\n     upgrades and integrations with other business applications &nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manage JDE batch scheduler</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: in