(27234, 400, 2636, 'description', '<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Description of Work:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Administration of PostgreSQL databases in Linux/Ubuntu Operating\r\nSystem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Provide support in managing database replication process between IOT\r\nand Amazon Web Services environments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Provide advice and support to PostgreSQL version upgrade and\r\nmigration process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Provide guidance in the creation and modification of standards and\r\nprocedures in utilizing PostgreSQL databases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Self-motivated person providing after hours support if necessary\r\nthrough the upgrade processes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Postgres Requirements: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Four+ years database administration and programing experiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; In depth knowledge of the PostgreSQL architecture and day-to-day\r\nadministration of PostgreSQL databases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; One+ recent years with PostgreSQL related WAL streaming replication\r\nand query monitoring tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Performance monitoring and capacity planning for PostgreSQL.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Support for system and database upgrades.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Solid understanding of RDBM concepts and normalization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Experience in managing multiple database servers, such as PostgreSQL\r\nand SQLServer databases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Experience in wr<a name="_GoBack"></a>iting queries for various\r\ndatabases, such as PostgreSQL and SQLServer databases using OpenQuery,\r\nLinkedServer, and db_link.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Experience with PostgreSQL tools such as PgAdmin III or higher\r\nversion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Experience setting up and managing PostgreSQL on AWS RDS is a plus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Linux/Ubuntu Requirements: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Proficiency in writing UNIX/Linux shell scripts (Korn and/or Bash).</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Proficiency in monitoring UNIX and PostgreSQL jobs and activities in\r\ndetermining performance issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; General understanding of Linux internals (system calls, file systems,\r\nprocesses, etc.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Install, configure, maintain, and troubleshooting hardware and\r\nUNIX/Linux serv