(27326, 400, 2574, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Scope\r\nof position</u></strong><u></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">We are seeking a senior software developer with at least 8\r\nyears&rsquo; experience in web application support and development with database\r\ndesign skills in a Microsoft .NET/SQL environment to join a highly skilled\r\nAgile team in a fast-paced environment converting legacy applications and\r\nsupporting existing ones.&nbsp; This candidate must have a strong development\r\nbackground developing and understanding solutions written in C# and strong\r\ndebugging skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Primary Responsibilities</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->8-10 years&rsquo; experience developing large systems\r\non the Microsoft stack.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience with Entity Framework, LINQ and\r\nLambda Expressions</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must be able to design, build, and maintain\r\nefficient, reusable, and reliable C# code</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience in cloud-based development\r\nenvironments</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience with contemporary REST/web services\r\ndevelopment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must have excellent interpersonal and\r\ncommunication skills both written and verbal with self-motivation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must be able to identify bottlenecks and bugs,\r\nand devise solutions to these problems </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span styl