ems and financial modules of packaged applications required </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Knowledge of designing and developing platform\r\nlevel components including event architectures, messaging a plus</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Desirable skills in applying Internet security\r\ndesign standards, knowledge of critical web application security\r\nvulnerabilities, able to design and develop highly secure web applications</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must have experience\r\nwith delivery of projects working in an<a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a> Agile Scrum\r\ndelivery framework</p>', NULL, '2017-06-08 08:49:46', 192, 1),
