(121237806, 400, 12121231, 'description', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">ESSENTIAL DUTIES</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">To perform this job successfully, an individual must be able to perform\r\neach essential duty satisfactorily.&nbsp;\r\nReasonable accommodation may be made to enable individuals with\r\ndisabilities to perform the essential functions.&nbsp; </span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Communicate and institutionalize security/compliance related\r\npolicies and standards.</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Drive\r\nsecurity/compliance training and awareness across the organization.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Work\r\ndirectly with external partners to implement technology, process and controls\r\nto ensure PCI compliance.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Perform\r\ninformation security assessments/audits of existing controls and processes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Gather\r\ndocumentation/technical information in support of audits and drive remediation\r\nefforts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provide\r\nconsultative advice to internal technical and development teams that enable\r\nthem to make informed risk management decisions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Maintain\r\nstrong working relationships with individuals and groups involved in managing\r\ninformation security risks across the organization.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Participate\r\nin moderate to highly complex projects as they pertain to the organization''s\r\nlong-term information security strategy.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provide\r\ndetailed risk and remediation guidelines, as well as perform remediation\r\nactivities where applicable.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Interpret\r\nbusiness requirements and functional specifications to recommend security\r\nrequirements</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Act\r\nas a Subject Matter Expert in the discovery and investigation of critical\r\nsecurity vulnerabilities as required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manage\r\nall Incident Response activities based on plan.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Work\r\nwith partners in conducting Vulnerability Scans and Penetration testing and drive\r\nremediation of identified gaps.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Take a lead role\r\n     in conducting security research on threats and remediation techniques/\r\n     technology, make recommendations to the <a name="_GoBack"></a>IT teams and\r\n     oversee implementation.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Serve as a\r\n     Compliance and Security Controls SME on internal/external requests for\r\n     security specific information.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Performs other duties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">REQUIRED KNOWLEDGE, SKILLS AND ABILITIES</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The requirements listed below are representative of the knowledge,\r\nskill, and/or ability necessary to perform this job.</span></em><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"> </span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">EDUCATION\r\nand/or EXPERIENCE</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">A\r\nBachelor''s degree in Computer Science, Information Security, or equivalent.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Proven competency with regulatory mandates such as GLBA, PCI and\r\nSOX.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Proven competency with risk management frameworks such as ISO\r\n27001, NIST or Cobit.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Strong\r\nknowledge and understanding of network architecture, application design,\r\nsystems engineering and integration.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\ndeveloping and managing remediation plans.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">2+ years'' experience in compliance or\r\nsecurity management with expertise in applying secure methods within system\r\ndevelopment lifecycle efforts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience conducting penetration tests and\r\nvulnerability scans.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Project management experience.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Knowledge of software development concepts\r\nand methodologies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Highly motivated, competitive,\r\nentrepreneurial and attracted to challenging opportunities</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to work in a fast-paced environment\r\nwhere organizational skills are essential</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Demonstrates strong problem solving,\r\nanalytical, interpersonal, and ownership skills</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Possess excellent collaboration skills with a\r\nwide variety of internal team members</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to interact with various technical\r\nand business partner teams.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Knowledge of network and application security\r\ntechnical controls and common vulnerabilities.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Competent in advanced communication skills\r\nincluding the ability to translate technical security concepts to business\r\noriented audiences.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Demonstrates ability to develop metrics,\r\nperform critical analysis and develop executive decision support content.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">LANGUAGE SKILLS</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Routinely\r\nreads, interprets and analyzes scientific and technical journals, complex\r\nfinancial reports, and/or legal documents.&nbsp;\r\nRoutinely responds to inquiries or complaints from customers, regulatory\r\nagencies, or members of the business community. &nbsp;Routinely presents information to top\r\nmanagement, public groups, and/or boards of directors.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">REASONING/PROBLEM SOLVING ABILITY</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Routinely\r\nanalyzes and defines problems, establishes facts, and draws valid\r\nconclusions.&nbsp; Able to deal with nonverbal\r\nsymbolism (formulas, scientific equations, graphs, etc.). Able to interpret an\r\nextensive variety of technical instructions/information in mathematical or\r\ndiagram form and deals with several abstract and non-concrete variables.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">DECISION\r\nMAKING &amp; IMPACT OF ERRORS</span></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Management &ndash;\r\nMakes decisions daily on use of resources, performance and budgets and in\r\nsupport of the organization&rsquo;s strategic direction. Decisions could require\r\nadditional expenditure of resources if not sound decisions. Decisions tend to\r\nbe short term (one year to three years) and usually moderate to high cost.<strong></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">PHYSICAL DEMANDS</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The physical demands described here are representative of those that\r\nmust be met by an employee to successfully perform the essential functions of\r\nthis job.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Able to\r\nstand and/or walk up to 35% of the time.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Able to sit over\r\n70% of the time.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">WORK ENVIRONMENT</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The work environment characteristics described here are representative\r\nof those an employee encounters while performing the essential functions of\r\nthis job.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Typically works in a general office\r\nenvironment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">TRAVEL REQUIREMENTS</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Travels up\r\nto 10% of the time.</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">ESSENTIAL DUTIES</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">To perform this job successfully, an individual must be able to perform\r\neach essential duty satisfactorily.&nbsp;\r\nReasonable accommodation may be made to enable individuals with\r\ndisabilities to perform the essential functions.&nbsp; </span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Communicate and institutionalize security/compliance related\r\npolicies and standards.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Drive\r\nsecurity/compliance training and awareness across the organization.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Work\r\ndirectly with external partners to implement technology, process and controls\r\nto ensure PCI compliance.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Perform\r\ninformation security assessments/audits of existing controls and processes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Gather\r\ndocumentation/technical information in support of audits and drive remediation\r\nefforts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provide\r\nconsultative advice to internal technical and development teams that enable\r\nthem to make informed risk management decisions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Maintain\r\nstrong working relationships with individuals and groups involved in managing\r\ninformation security risks across the organization.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Participate\r\nin moderate to highly complex projects as they pertain to the organization''s\r\nlong-term information security strategy.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provide\r\ndetailed risk and remediation guidelines, as well as perform remediation\r\nactivities where applicable.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Interpret\r\nbusiness requirements and functional specifications to recommend security\r\nrequirements</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Act\r\nas a Subject Matter Expert in the discovery and investigation of critical\r\nsecurity vulnerabilities as required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manage\r\nall Incident Response activities based on plan.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Work\r\nwith partners in conducting Vulnerability Scans and Penetration testing and drive\r\nremediation of identified gaps.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Take a lead role\r\n     in conducting security research on threats and remediation techniques/\r\n     technology, make recommendations to the <a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a>IT teams and\r\n     oversee implementation.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Serve as a\r\n     Compliance and Security Controls SME on internal/external requests for\r\n     security specific information.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Performs other duties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">REQUIRED KNOWLEDGE, SKILLS AND ABILITIES</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The requirements listed below are representative of the knowledge,\r\nskill, and/or ability necessary to perform this job.</span></em><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"> </span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">EDUCATION\r\nand/or EXPERIENCE</span></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">A\r\nBachelor''s degree in Computer Science, Information Security, or equivalent.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Proven competency with regulatory mandates such as GLBA, PCI and\r\nSOX.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Proven competency with risk management frameworks such as ISO\r\n27001, NIST or Cobit.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Strong\r\nknowledge and understanding of network architecture, application design,\r\nsystems engineering and integration.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\ndeveloping and managing remediation plans.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">2+ years'' experience in compliance or\r\nsecurity management with expertise in applying secure methods within system\r\ndevelopment lifecycle efforts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience conducting penetration tests and\r\nvulnerability scans.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span