-0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Demonstrates strong problem solving,\r\nanalytical, interpersonal, and ownership skills</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Possess excellent collaboration skills with a\r\nwide variety of internal team members</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to interact with various technical\r\nand business partner teams.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 107%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-va