(121238156, 400, 12121254, 'description', '<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Salesforce BA</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">The Lead Analyst, Analytics assist in driving business\r\ninitiatives and analytics by leveraging Salesforce.com, Marketing Cloud,\r\nTableau and other Business Intelligence tools. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">The Lead Analyst will have opportunity to apply thoughtful\r\nbusiness and technical acumen across projects and tasks. Additionally, the role\r\nwill lead sales and marketing partnerships in driving sales efforts and bottom\r\nline results. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">The role will be require the ability address complex data\r\nanalysis and reporting, such as those associated to DOL regulatory needs for\r\ninternal and external clients. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Salesforce.com user and administrative knowledge (or\r\nsimilar), Tableau or equivalent Business Intelligence tools, Strong MS Office\r\nskills, particularly in Excel. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Excellent analytical skills with the ability to communicate\r\ncomplex concepts succinctly, Strong knowledge of the business and how\r\ndashboards can assist leaders in driving strategy. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Primary accountability is to maintain Business Intelligence\r\ntools inclusive of Salesforce.com, Marketing Cloud and Tableau dashboards to\r\nprovide leaders consistent, accurate insight to make strategic business\r\ndecisions, meet regulatory requirements and execute on business opportunities. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Lead Analysts is expected to master the underlying data and\r\nbecome a &quot;go to&quot; resource for data questions and resolution,\r\nincluding providing future solutions. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Primary accountability is to maintain Business Intelligence\r\ntools inclusive of Salesforce.com, Marketing Cloud and Tableau dashboards to\r\nprovide leaders consistent, accurate insight to make strategic business\r\ndecisions, meet regulatory requirements and execute on business opportunities. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Lead Analysts is expected to master the underlying data and\r\nbecome a &quot;go to&quot; resource for data questions and resolution,\r\nincluding providing future solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Under direction of team leaders, Lead Analyst will create\r\nad-hoc analysis based on specific business queries. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">The analysis performed may drive the development of future\r\ndashboards and creation of business requirements for additional data feeds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">As a Marketing liaison, participate in ongoing Business,\r\nTechnology, Finance meetings to ensure deployment pipeline aligns with\r\nMarketing Cloud (and other Marketing business technology) needs. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Incumbent will manage BME (change control) where Marketing\r\ntools impact SFDC or other connected business managed technologies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Provide guidance on necessary metrics from Marketing Cloud\r\ndriven programs, including the design of Tableau dashboards to share results\r\nbroadly. Ability to articulate metrics needed by varying level from Senior\r\nLeadership to Internal Sales Desk.</p>', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Client &ndash; Columbia Threadneedle</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>4-6 month duration in Boston</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Person does not have to be local will hire off skype</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Start date is ASAP</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Marketing Cloud developer (Salesforce). </strong></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Hands on 5+ years in Salesforce</strong>.</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">Here are the key skills:-</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><ul style="margin-top: 0in">\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">AMPscript, html,\r\n     javascript</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Experience with setting up\r\n     &ldquo;custom&rdquo; subscription center</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Data Extensions</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Interactions (Triggered\r\n     emails, user initiated sends etc.)</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Activities (Queries,\r\n     Imports, Data extracts etc.)</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">API</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Integrations - Web\r\n     analytics </li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Integrations &ndash; CRM\r\n     (campaign)</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="background: yellow">marketingcloud v5 integration experience</span></strong></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">contact builder/audience\r\n     builder &ndash; contacts configuration</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Automation Studio</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Journey Builder and\r\n     interactions</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Experience with Dynamic\r\n     content (amp script etc)</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, '2017-07-06 16:13:07', 192, 1),
